body:
Hello Splade here and I just wanted to let you know that I make intros for youtube channels! No templates used whatsoever! If you would like an intro add me on skype and tell me why you'd like one! Down below are some examples of intros I have made for people in the past! Please keep in mind that one intro will take around 2 days to 1 week depending on how busy I am :P

MLGtino: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JSAuGRZ25U0&list=UUGdctIIC6VNWisslv2fOIQA

EmeraldSword85: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AaY8uo4E_3E&list=UUGdctIIC6VNWisslv2fOIQA&index=8

AwarriorVenom/Exzyy: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I-yoOLvrHX8&list=UUGdctIIC6VNWisslv2fOIQA

Splade4812:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kJdp8TygkPQ&list=UUGdctIIC6VNWisslv2fOIQA
